      "content": "DONE — activity-recording restructure\n\n**Files changed:**\n- `src/mcp-server.ts` (+6/-2): added `agent_id` param to `start_activity` schema; handler uses `agent_id ?? AGENT_ID`\n- `src/db.ts` (+8/-2): `attachCommitToCurrentActivity` SQL now `ORDER BY (agent_id = ?) DESC, started_at DESC` — prefers committer's activity, falls back to most recent in-progress across all agents; added JSDoc\n- `templates/SYNAPSE-worker.md` (+5/-7): removed `start_activity` (step 2) and `finish_activity` (step 5) from per-task workflow; removed \"finish the activity normally\" from blocked recovery\n- `templates/SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md` (+12/0): added \"Recording task activities\" section with the send → start_activity → DONE → commit → finish_activity flow, plus self-driven variant\n\n**Build:** `bun run build` → clean\n\n**New orchestrator workflow:** `send_message` task → `start_activity({agent_id: worker})` → wait for DONE → `git commit` → `finish_activity`. Activity is still `in_progress` at commit time so the hook's in-progress lookup attaches the SHA correctly; `finish_activity` closes it after.\n\n**Self-driven case still works:** calling `start_activity` without `agent_id` defaults to the calling agent (orchestrator), same behaviour as before.",
